-----------------------------------------
 Pairing Based Cryptography
-----------------------------------------

[Description]

PBCL : Library of pairing computation on elliptic curve
BB1  : Sample program of identity based encryption with PBCL

[command memo]

$ git clone git://github.com/Pollucca/PBC.git
$ cd PBC/PBCL-x.x
$ ant
$ cd ../BB1
$ mkdir bb1; mkdir lib
$ cp ../PBCL-x.x/pbcl-x.x.jar lib/
$ ant
$ java -jar bb1-x.x.jar


 
